      public static void navigateScreens(String path, javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent, String stageTitle) throws IOException

      Parameters:
      path - the screen to navigate to
      actionEvent - the actionEvent passed on from the button click
      stageTitle - the stage title of the screen to navigate to
      Throws:
      IOException - exception thrown when the screen changes
